.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>해결:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>터널링 상태 확인:\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">netstat</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-an</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">grep</span> <span class=\"token number\">3306</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>다른 포트를 사용해 충돌 방지:\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">ssh</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-i</span> aws-key.pem <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-L</span> <span class=\"token number\">3307</span>:mydb.xxxxx.us-east-1.rds.amazonaws.com:3306 ec2-user@54.123.45.67</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"요약\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9A%94%EC%95%BD\" aria-label=\"요약 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>요약</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><strong>EC2에 SSH 접속</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">ssh</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-i</span> aws-key.pem ec2-user@54.123.45.67</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>EC2에서 RDS 연결 테스트</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">mysql <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-h</span> mydb.xxxxx.us-east-1.rds.amazonaws.com <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-P</span> <span class=\"token number\">3306</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-u</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>db_user<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-p</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>SSH 터널링 설정</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">ssh</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-i</span> aws-key.pem <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-L</span> <span class=\"token number\">3306</span>:mydb.xxxxx.us-east-1.rds.amazonaws.com:3306 ec2-user@54.123.45.67</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>로컬에서 데이터베이스 접속</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">mysql <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-h</span> <span class=\"token number\">127.0</span>.0.1 <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-P</span> <span class=\"token number\">3306</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-u</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>db_user<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-p</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"참고-자료\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0-%EC%9E%90%EB%A3%8C\" aria-label=\"참고 자료 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>참고 자료</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>AWS EC2 문서</li>\n<li>AWS RDS 문서</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"AWS EC2를 통해 RDS SSH 터널링 설정 가이드","date":"December 13, 2024","update":null,"tags":["AWS","RDS"],"series":"AWS 보안 시리즈"},"fields":{"slug":"/AWS_EC2_to_RDS_Tunneling_Guide_KR/","readingTime":{"minutes":4.22}}},"seriesList":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"f3086d7f-abcf-5946-abb7-09bb2255eaab","fields":{"slug":"/AWS_EC2_to_RDS_Tunneling_Guide_KR/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"AWS EC2를 통해 RDS SSH 터널링 설정 가이드"}}}]},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/protobuf-grpc-guide/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Protocol Buffers와 gRPC 설정 가이드"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/windows-venv-guide/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Windows 가상 환경(venv) 활성화 문제 해결 가이드"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"f3086d7f-abcf-5946-abb7-09bb2255eaab","series":"AWS 보안 시리즈","pre